{"id":10451,"date":"2022-09-01T11:06:50","date_gmt":"2022-09-01T05:36:50","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/?p=10451"},"modified":"2022-09-01T11:06:50","modified_gmt":"2022-09-01T05:36:50","slug":"build-question-answer-website-like-quora","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/build-question-answer-website-like-quora.html","title":{"rendered":"Guide to Building a Question and Answer Site Like Quora"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-10452 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Quora_like_website_hiddenbrains.jpg\" alt=\"website-like-quora\" width=\"908\" height=\"441\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Quora_like_website_hiddenbrains.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Quora_like_website_hiddenbrains-300x146.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/Quora_like_website_hiddenbrains-768x373.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a new world of information sharing, and we have been drawn to sites like Quora that allow users to ask questions and then answer those questions by other users with relevant expertise. Questions can be requested by anyone and answered by anyone with sufficient knowledge on the subject of the question.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you want to build such a site but need some help getting started, this guide will show you how to build website like Quora from scratch. It is important that you partner with a trusted agency providing end-to-end web application development services.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_is_Quora\"><\/span><b>What is Quora?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Founded in 2009, Quora is a social question-and-answer website to collaborate by editing questions and commenting on answers submitted by other users. With almost 300 million users a month, Quora is a goliath of information sharing and a benchmark for success.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quora_Quick_Stats\"><\/span><b>Quora: Quick Stats<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quora has 300+ million monthly active users<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The majority of Quora users are from 18 to 24<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The average time spent by a user on the platform is around 8-10 minutes<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3000 to 5000 Questions are asked on the platform every day<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Men users access the platform more<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Why_is_Quora_so_popular\"><\/span><b>Why is Quora so popular?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you have a question, you go to Quora and either search for an answer or ask your question. If you search for an answer, you&#8217;ll see a list of questions related to your query, as well as the top solution for each question. Also, other users can answer your own question or offer their own insights if you ask your own question.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can also upvote or downvote questions and answers, which helps surface the most popular content.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In a nutshell, here are a few reasons why Quora is so popular:<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A great resource for finding answers to questions you may have.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Great way to connect with like-minded people.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A platform for promoting your business or website.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build up your credibility as an expert in your field.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Generate traffic to your website or blog.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build backlinks to your website or blog.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Raise brand awareness to get people talking about your brand or product.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ask community questions, even if experts do not answer them in the subject matter.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Answering questions can help them gain recognition and support businesses.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Build brands and attract new followers on social media channels.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Learn more about what people think about topics related to your industry or niche topic.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Business_model_of_Q_A_Site_like_Quora\"><\/span><b>Business model of Q&amp;A Site like Quora<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A question-and-answer website like Quora typically generates revenue through advertising. Content is user-generated, meaning the site does not have to create its content. Instead, it relies on its users to generate content.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This content is used to attract visitors to the site, who are shown ads. The site may also sell access to its user data and offer premium features that allow users to get more out of the site.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Key_features_of_a_question-and-answer_website\"><\/span><b>Key features of a question-and-answer website<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A question-and-answer website like Quora allows users to ask and answer questions on any topic. The site typically has a search function so users can easily find answers to their questions. In addition, the site may also have features like upvoting and downvoting, tagging, commenting, and social media integration. A question-and-answer website is a great way to build an online community around a particular topic or interest. If you have any further ideas to build website like Quora, you partner with a development agency, specializing in providing <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/web-application-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">web application development services<\/a> for advance needs.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Search page&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Search for any questions, answers or topics on Quora<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Monitor questions<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Manage Topics<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Answer Change Log<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">User endorsements page<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Redirecting questions and answers<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mark as best answer<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Editing questions and question details<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Users profiles<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Activity feed<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Following topics<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Social media sharing<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Internal messaging system<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_build_your_own_Q_A_website\"><\/span><b>How to build your own Q&amp;A website?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Quora has become one of the most well-known sites on the Internet in recent years, and its tremendous success has inspired many startups to follow in its footsteps. But how do you build your question-and-answer site? How do you create a compelling website that users will love?&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">And what can you do to guarantee your site becomes as successful as Quora?&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To answer these questions, we&#8217;ll look at some elements to build website like Quora, and how you can apply this knowledge to build your successful question-and-answer site.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Step_by_step_guide_to_build_Quora_like_website\"><\/span><b>Step by step guide to build Quora like website&nbsp;<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Creating an online Q&amp;A platform takes some work, but it&#8217;s worth it if you&#8217;re looking for more engagement with your customers.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"a_Discovery_Planning\"><\/span><b>a) Discovery &amp; Planning<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This critical phase involves complete research and planning that will create a strong foundation for your site. There are several questions that you should answer which will become a part of your strategy.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>What is the objective? Who is your target audience? Are you looking for large-scale traffic or personal, more intimate discussions? What will you do with the information they provide?<\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How many questions will there be on the site, what are their topics, which should be able to ask and answer them, and how often should new questions be added?<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">How will you reward users of your website (points, badges, reputations) and keep people coming back? <\/span><\/li>\n<li>Will this be an informative site, or will you offer products for sale too?<\/li>\n<li>Is it appropriate to use other people&#8217;s content without permission, such as copying and pasting articles from Wikipedia?<\/li>\n<li>Who should own the intellectual property rights over any text created by other users on your website &#8211; yourself or the authors of that content?<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"b_Create_a_user-friendly_and_intuitive_design\"><\/span><b>b) Create a user-friendly and intuitive design<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the first things you need to decide on is the design. It&#8217;s important for your site design to be easy for people to use and navigate. Otherwise, you&#8217;ll have a very low percentage of visitors taking time out of their day to participate in what you have available.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Think about how someone will search for an answer &#8211; it should be simple with specific keywords. Don&#8217;t overcomplicate your layout with information that doesn&#8217;t matter because it&#8217;ll distract from the content that does matter.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"c_Development\"><\/span><b>c) Development&nbsp;<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Now is the time to transform your research, planning, and intuitive design into reality with the development stage. You can avail web development services to build a custom question and answer website that totally reflects your brand identity. A custom solution can easily grow as your site changes and gains market traction.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"d_Launching_the_Website\"><\/span><b>d) Launching the Website<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To start your website, you need to register the domain name and find a hosting company. You also need to set up databases for your site, which will serve as the backbone of your website. Databases are created using MySQL or Microsoft SQL Server or cloud-based services such as Amazon RDS (AWS).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you have time and are skilled with code, setting up the database may save money because you&#8217;ll have fewer monthly hosting fees with this option.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_much_does_it_cost_to_build_a_site_like_Quora\"><\/span><b>How much does it cost to build a site like Quora?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you&#8217;re looking to build a website like Quora, you&#8217;ll need to invest in some software and hosting costs. Depending on the features you want to include, your development costs could vary significantly. Plus, you&#8217;ll need to factor in hosting costs, as well as the expertise of your team.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To create a Q &amp; A site, you need to hire a team of web developers, which will include the following specialists:<\/span><\/em><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Project Manager: Oversee all aspects of project management during the development lifecycle and delivery. Project Manager\/ SPOC will coordinate with onshore and offshore teams.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">UX\/UI designer: Manage diverse aspects related to design and UI\/UX development.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">iOS\/Android developers: Smartphone users prefer to use the service using an application rather than a browser.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Backend developers: Expertise in creating the &#8220;server&#8221; part of the site.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Frontend developers: Responsible for implementing software that interacts with users.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">QA Engineer: Conduct quality assurance checks to ensure a seamless experience across devices.&nbsp;<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\